node.text: I am very proud to announce that I am the ambassador of the European Amputee Football Championship, which will take place in September 2020 in #Kraków #Poland ⚽🏆. I hope it will be a great tournament full of great and positive emotions.  Huge respect for all players👏🤜🤛 #AmpFutbol #AmpEURO2020 #EqualGame @ampfutbol 🎥 @stor9_

node.text: Kuba is struggling with a serious knee injury for the second time, but he is doing everything to come back even stronger👏🙌⚽. When I was young I had a similar experience, so I know how important it is to keep your head up and fight regardless of the obstacles💪🙅🏻‍♂️ #AkademiaPewnościSiebie #KeepYourHeadUp #PodniesGlowe @headandshoulderseu #ad
